**Otherwise** (player is alive and in the game): When a mob is present in the Current room, include at least one combat option (e.g. kill goblin); when a corpse is present, include a looting action (e.g. get all corpse). When a door was reported closed, include open door (e.g. open door east). Do not suggest kill or get all corpse unless the Current room actually lists a mob or corpse. Example (exactly 5 actions; use only what fits the actual Current room):
